                "title": "售後服務彈"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>治療我方出戰角色2點，並使其獲得1點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">充能</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/18/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_8716100488440790263.png",
